OL,3,CFA issues historic apology to
OL,4,Cpioneering women's football team
OL,6,FThe Football Association (FA) has
OL,7,Fissued a landmark apology to the
OL,8,Fpioneering women's football team who
OL,9,Fdefied a 50-year ban on the sport
OL,10,Fduring the 20th century.
OL,12,FOriginating in Didsbury in 1949, the
OL,13,FManchester Corinthians Ladies FC
OL,14,Femerged at the peak of the FA's ban on
OL,15,Fwomen's football which barred female
OL,16,Fteams from using any official,
OL,17,Faffiliated grounds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
