CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774379485
OL,3,CFA issues historic apology to
OL,4,Cpioneering women's football team
OL,6,FThey defied the ban by playing charity
OL,7,Fgames at home and overseas, ultimately
OL,8,Flaying the foundations for the rise of
OL,9,Fthe woman's game.
OL,11,FWhile they were largely ignored or
OL,12,Fridiculed in the UK, they were treated
OL,13,Flike celebrities abroad and even
OL,14,Fembarked on massive international
OL,15,Ftours and won more than 50 trophies.
OL,17,FThe FA has now formally apologised to
OL,18,Fthe women, whose stories are told in a
OL,19,Fnew documentary - "The Corinthians: We
OL,20,FWere the Champions".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
