PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774379485
OL,3,CFA issues historic apology to
OL,4,Cpioneering women's football team
OL,6,FThe governing body said it is sorry
OL,7,Ffor the 50-year ban on women's
OL,8,Ffootball, honouring the Manchester
OL,9,FCorinthians for their "unwavering
OL,10,Fspirit and determination".
OL,12,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"We are sorry that a ban on women's
OL,14,Ffootball was introduced in 1921 and
OL,15,Fnot revoked until 1971.
OL,17,F"We recognise the courage of the teams
OL,18,Fand individuals who continued to play
OL,19,Fthe game during this period.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
