CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774379485
OL,3,CFA issues historic apology to
OL,4,Cpioneering women's football team
OL,6,F"In more recent times, our ongoing
OL,7,Fcommitment and investment into women's
OL,8,Fand girls' football in England has
OL,9,Fachieved unprecedented success and
OL,10,Fgrowth across all levels of the game `
OL,11,Fand we will ensure it continues to
OL,12,Fthrive in the future."
OL,14,FTheir is told in a new documentary for
OL,15,FThe Corinthians: We Were The
OL,16,FChampions, Films Not Words
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
