CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774379485
OL,3,CFA issues historic apology to
OL,4,Cpioneering women's football team
OL,6,FOften described as the "football
OL,7,Fsuffragettes", The Corinthians were
OL,8,Fpioneers of the women's game,
OL,9,Fproceeding the success of The
OL,10,FLionesses, yet their story has been
OL,11,Fall but forgotten.
OL,13,FThe players defied the ban on women
OL,14,Fplaying football by playing charity
OL,15,Fgames at home and overseas
OL,17,FSome of their matches attracted crowds
OL,18,Fof tens of thousands in massive
OL,19,Fstadiums, including Sporting Lisbon,
OL,20,Fand large amounts were raised for
OL,21,Fcharity.
OL,26,@oD@MO]
